  "arbitrary": [
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Simplex method for  linear programming"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The "
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "simplex"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " method uses a traditional, full-tableau implementation of Dantzig's simplex algorithm ,  ("
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "not"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " the Nelder-Mead simplex). This algorithm is included for backwards compatibility and educational purposes."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "value": "versionadded 0.15.0"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "admonitionTitle"
                }
              ],
              "kind": "note",
              "type": "admonition"
            }
          ],
          "type": "blockquote"
        }
      ],
      "level": 0,
      "target": null,
      "title": null,
      "type": "Section"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The simplex method may encounter numerical difficulties when pivot values are close to the specified tolerance. If encountered try remove any redundant constraints, change the pivot strategy to Bland's rule or increase the tolerance value."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Alternatively, more robust methods maybe be used. See "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "'interior-point' <optimize.linprog-interior-point>"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "'revised simplex' <optimize.linprog-revised_simplex>"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "level": 0,
      "target": null,
      "title": "Warnings",
      "type": "Section"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "placeholder": "footnote",
